snippet.title: Suriya & Lokesh Kanagaraj | Ananda Vikatan Cinema Awards🏆 2020 - 21, 2022 | Vikatan Awards | Part 04
snippet.description:
#lokeshkanagaraj #suriya #jaibhim  #avcinemaawards #vikatanawards #cinemavikatan #Vikatancinemaawards  

Welcome to the prestigious Vikatan Cinema Awards Function! This annual event celebrates excellence in the world of cinema, with awards being presented to the best of the best in Tamil cinema over the past three years - 2020, 2021, and 2022. Join us as we recognize the outstanding achievements of our talented actors, actresses, directors, and technicians, who have captivated audiences with their exceptional work. The awards ceremony promises to be an unforgettable evening, filled with glamour, excitement, and emotion. Watch as the winners are announced and receive their awards from our esteemed presenters. From Best Actor and Best Actress to Best Director and Best Music Director, the competition is fierce and the talent is exceptional. So, sit back, relax, and enjoy the show as we celebrate the magic of cinema and honour the best of the best at the Vikatan Cinema Awards Function.

ICYM

Part 02: https://youtu.be/qlIVTV3piz0
Part 03: https://youtu.be/RSP1IPdvVhg

snippet.title: 1 Year For KGF Chapter 2 | Yash | Prashanth Neel | Vijay Kiragandur | Sanjay Dutt | Hombale Films
snippet.description:
One year ago today, #KGFChapter2 took us on an unforgettable journey filled with breathtaking action, intense emotions and larger-than-life characters. The film's release was nothing short of a festival, with fans celebrating in theaters around the world. We're humbled by the incredible response to the film and grateful to everyone who made it such a success. Here's to the power of storytelling and the magic of cinema!

#1ROCKYingYearOfKGF2

Written and Directed by Prashanth Neel
Produced by Vijay Kiragandur under the Banner "Hombale Films".
Starring: Rocking Star Yash, Sanjay Dutt, Srinidhi Shetty, Raveena Tandon, Prakash Raj, Malvika Avinash, Achyuth Kumar, Ayyappa P. Sharma, Rao Ramesh, Eshwari Rao, Archana Jois, T. S. snippet.title: Allu Arha as Prince Bharata - Telugu Promo | Shaakuntalam | Samantha | Gunasekhar| Dil Raju
snippet.description:
Shaakuntalam Movie also in 3D, Written & Directed by Gunasekhar, Presented by Dil Raju under Sri Venkateswara Creations in collaboration with Gunaa Teamworks, Produced by Neelima Guna.

The massively mounted film Shaakuntalam based on internationally acclaimed Kalidasa’s Sanskrit play ‘Abhijnana Shakuntalam’ is all set to release in Hindi, Telugu, Tamil, Malayalam & Kannada.  The story of Shaakuntalam revolves around the epic love story of Shakuntala and King Dushyant from Mahabharata, portrayed by Samantha and Dev Mohan.

The film is helmed by supremely proficient, Director Gunasekhar and marks a whimsical tale of love set in the Kashyapa Kanumalu (Kashmir), the grandeur and splendour of Dushyant’s Puru Dynasty making the film extremely exceptional.

Cast and Crew Details: 

Shaakuntalam starring Samantha, Dev Mohan, Allu Arha, Sachin Khedekar, Kabir Bedi, Dr.M Mohan Babu, Prakash Raj, Madhubala, Gautami, Aditi Balan, Ananya Nagalla, Jisshu Sengupta and others

snippet.title: WATERMELON CHICKEN | Chicken Cooked in Watermelon Fruits | Country Chicken Gravy in Watermelon
snippet.description:
Today in our village, we cook country chicken gravy with using watermelons instead of vessels. Cooking chicken recipe in watermelon is always challenging because these are cook both at same time. But the heat will pass quickly to the chicken so we can cook easily.

The taste looks like coconut chicken, but its yummy!

Dhyan Sreenivasan is an Indian actor, and film director who works in Malayalam films.Dhyan Sreenivasan was born on December 20, 1988 in Thalassery, Kerala, India. Dhyan Sreenivasan made his acting debut with Thira, directed by Dhyan Sreenivasan elder brother Vineeth Sreenivasan. Dhyan is the younger son of noted actor and screenwriter Sreenivasan. Dhyan Sreenivasan brother Vineeth Sreenivasan is a singer, actor and director who also works in Malayalam cinema. Dhyan married his longtime girlfriend Arpita Sebastian on 7 April 2017. He made his film debut with the Malayalam film Thira which has Shobana in main lead role. In the film, Dhyan Sreenivasan did a supporting role along with two-time National Award winning actress Shobana. His performance in the film was generally well-received by critics and the audience.

snippet.description:
#avcinemaawards #vikatanawards #cinemavikatan #Vikatancinemaawards #parthiban  

Welcome to the prestigious Vikatan Cinema Awards Function! This annual event celebrates excellence in the world of cinema, with awards being presented to the best of the best in Tamil cinema over the past three years - 2020, 2021, and 2022. Join us as we recognize the outstanding achievements of our talented actors, actresses, directors, and technicians, who have captivated audiences with their exceptional work. The awards ceremony promises to be an unforgettable evening, filled with glamour, excitement, and emotion. Watch as the winners are announced and receive their awards from our esteemed presenters. From Best Actor and Best Actress to Best Director and Best Music Director, the competition is fierce and the talent is exceptional. So, sit back, relax, and enjoy the show as we celebrate the magic of cinema and honour the best of the best at the Vikatan Cinema Awards Function.

snippet.title: Death Threats, Sidhu Moose Wala & SRK's Support - @YoYoHoneySingh  | Figuring Out | EP 85
snippet.description:
Order my first book 'Build, Don't Talk' here: https://amzn.eu/d/eCfijRu

--------------
In today’s episode of Figuring Out, Raj talks with Honey Singh, AKA Hirdesh Singh an Indian music producer, rapper, singer, songwriter and an actor and has been widely loved in the Hindi as well as Punjabi Film Industry. Hailing from Delhi,  Singh prefers to sing in Hindi and his native language Punjabii rather than English.

Singh shares how his life is a manifestation of what he wanted it to be like and how he’s been blessed to have received mentorship & support from the who’s who of the industry like Shah Rukh Khan, Salman Khan, Akshay Kumar, & Amitabh Bachchan. 

Honey Singh has finally broken his silence for the first time ever on ‘Mafia Mundeer’, a group of boys he made music with back in Punjab and the reasons behind breaking it off. 


Having gone through a tough journey of Bipolar Disorder, Singh speaks openly about dealing with mental illness, his symptoms, treatment and the struggle he went through during this time. 

Make sure you watch this video till the end!


-------------------------

🎧 Stream Figuring Out episodes on Spotify: 
https://open.spotify.com/show/736rhmW7vilNgkFFo8aDz4

📺 Watch Figuring Out episodes on YouTube:
https://youtube.com/playlist?list=PLE0Jo6NF_JYO5-phess8GKafKMtPv3tfZ

-------------

localized.title: Death Threats, Sidhu Moose Wala & SRK's Support - @YoYoHoneySingh  | Figuring Out | EP 85
localized.description:
Order my first book 'Build, Don't Talk' here: https://amzn.eu/d/eCfijRu

--------------
In today’s episode of Figuring Out, Raj talks with Honey Singh, AKA Hirdesh Singh an Indian music producer, rapper, singer, songwriter and an actor and has been widely loved in the Hindi as well as Punjabi Film Industry. Hailing from Delhi,  Singh prefers to sing in Hindi and his native language Punjabii rather than English.

Singh shares how his life is a manifestation of what he wanted it to be like and how he’s been blessed to have received mentorship & support from the who’s who of the industry like Shah Rukh Khan, Salman Khan, Akshay Kumar, & Amitabh Bachchan. 

Honey Singh has finally broken his silence for the first time ever on ‘Mafia Mundeer’, a group of boys he made music with back in Punjab and the reasons behind breaking it off. 


Having gone through a tough journey of Bipolar Disorder, Singh speaks openly about dealing with mental illness, his symptoms, treatment and the struggle he went through during this time. 

Make sure you watch this video till the end!

snippet.description:
Discussion on food is going on and there is no sign regarding its end. In the middle of the ongoing debate, Champaklal places his point of preparing normal and healthy food for all as food is necessary to live. Can the preparation for food will be completed in time? Why Babita is worried? Stay tuned and watch the full episode.

Episode No: 1799
Produced By: Asit Kumar Modi

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story evolves around happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi), an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Sailesh Lodha), is his neighbour. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble for all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son, he calls his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal. 

Click here to watch more episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL6Rtnh6YJK7b_jX6oY-D1z70o2IqE81FS

snippet.title: மதுரை பரோட்டா சால்னா | Madurai Famous Parotta Salna Recipe | CDK 1179 | Chef Deena's Kitchen
snippet.description:
Parotta Salna
INGREDIENTS  

Groundnut Oil – 400 ml
Shallots – ½ Kg
Green Chilli – 20 Nos
Whole Garam Mixed (Bay Leaf, Cinnamon Sticks, Cloves, Kalpasi, Cardamom – 15gm)
Ginger Paste – 1 Ladle
Garlic Paste – 3 Ladle
Country Tomato – 500 G
Mint – 2 Hand Full
Coriander – 1 Hand Full
Mutton With Bones – 1 Kg
Mutton Fat – 200 G
Curry Leaves  - As Required 
Turmeric Powder  - 3 Tsp
Cumin Powder – 3 Ladle
Fennel Powder – 2 Tsp
Pepper Powder – 5 Tsp
 Coriander Powder – 1 Ladle
Red Chilli Powder – ½ Ladle
Chilli Powder – 1 Ladle
Salt – As Required
Coconut – 8 Nos
Peanut – 50 G
Roasted Channa – 50 G
Coconut Milk – 1 Ladle
Nutmeg Powder – ½ piece

►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

snippet.title: Farq Last Episode Teaser - 17th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Farq Last Episode Teaser - 17th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Farq is the story of two different individuals, Irsa (Sehar Khan) and Kamal (Faysal Quraishi) who come together to form an unusual union under compromising circumstances. 
From the outside, Irsa and Kamal seem not to be made for each other. They are too different in terms of character, life choices, desires and socio-economic background. 
On one hand, Irsa desires to live a life of luxury while Kamal is fed up with the loneliness that his house offers. Despite being together as a couple, 
will the two ever look at the truth in themselves to determine who they are and what they want in life?

Written By: Imran Nazir
Directed By: Aehsun Talish
Produced By: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Faysal Quraishi as Kamal Hassan
Sehar Khan as Irsa 
Adeel Chaudhry as Daniyal
Mahmood Aslam as Arif
Saba Shah as Ayzel
Juvaria Abbasi as Faiza

Farq Last Episode Teaser - 17th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Farq is the story of two different individuals, Irsa (Sehar Khan) and Kamal (Faysal Quraishi) who come together to form an unusual union under compromising circumstances. 
From the outside, Irsa and Kamal seem not to be made for each other. They are too different in terms of character, life choices, desires and socio-economic background. 
On one hand, Irsa desires to live a life of luxury while Kamal is fed up with the loneliness that his house offers. Despite being together as a couple, 
will the two ever look at the truth in themselves to determine who they are and what they want in life?

snippet.description:
Check NEET Maha Revision 2023 👉🏻 https://smart.link/0wneffoeqmlzu

Lakshya NEET 2024: https://smart.link/mn8o1ogg5w6sd
YAKEEN (Dropper NEET) 2024 - https://smart.link/5d90w6wew1g2f
Arjuna NEET 2024 - https://smart.link/ecco57rlszrim 

Batch Details : 
- We will cover Botany, Zoology, Physics, Organic Chemistry, Inorganic Chemistry, and Physical Chemistry in One Shot

- One Shot Marathon series will start on Physics wallah - Alakh Pandey Channel on 19th April 2023

- Then, Subject wise Master MCQ Marathon series will be continue on Competition Wallah YouTube Channel on 26th April 2023

- At the end, 5 Live AITS (All India Test Series) Live Discussion on Competition Wallah YouTube Channel

- After NEET 2023 Exam, the Live Paper Discussion will also be scheduled on Competition Wallah YouTube Channel at the same day.

- Lecture notes will be available on NEET Maha Revision 2023 Batch (PW App)

- The complete course will be accessible to all the students until the NEET 2023 Exams

- Marathon Schedule will be provided in the community post of Competition Wallah YT Channel and Announcement section of the PW App

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

snippet.title: Tere Bin Episode 33 Teaser - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 33 Teaser - 13th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

#arvindkejriwal   #delhividhansabhaelection2020  #livehindustan 

Arvind Kejriwal Delhi Vidhan Sabha Speech: CBI की पूछताछ के बाद केजरीवाल का विधानसभा में भाषण 

शराब घोटाला मामले में सीएम केजरीवाल से सीबीआई की पूछताछ को लेकर आम आदमी पार्टी बीजेपी पर हमलावर है. दिल्ली विधानसभा का आज स्पेशल सत्र बुलाया गया था. सदन में केजरीवाल ने जोरदार भाषण दिया

snippet.description:
Brown Town Music & Nav Sandhu Presents New Punjabi Song Routine By Gur Sidhu Ft Jasmine Sandlas.

Listen to Routine song on all audio streaming platforms:

👉 Spotify: https://gursidhu.bfan.link/routine-3/spotify

Track Credits:-
Song: Routine
Singer: Gur Sidhu Ft Jasmine Sandlas

Music: Gur Sidhu

Makeup  - Addy 
Costume  - Sruishty Juneja 

Team Jasmine Sandlas :
Hair - Ishan 
Makeup - Addy 
Costume - Priyana thappar
Management - Vaani Jindal

LYRICS:-

Main bathinde di cream te tu cali di queen ae
Krta scan billo jihnu kitta seen ae
Akh vich fire aa te cup ch caffine ae
Munda lagge zehar te tu lagdi zareen ae
Two face duniya imaan te na deen ae
Jo nal yakke turde aa ohna te yakeen ae
Golden kartoos russia di been ae
Khulli aa zmeen billo khulli beggy jean ae
Tuckin shirt aa te lagda shokeen ae

Ni ehtan sada regular mitthiye routine ae x4

Nakhro te noor poora husan hseen ae
Offran tan aoungiya kudi aafreen ae
Tim tim krdi ve age haale teen ae
Jhaaka mera jhaaka jatta surgan da scene ae
Scene j bnaunda jehda kr lainda seen ae
Dirty ja dekhda a teri ki skeem ae
Bhrr peg naina cho j lggea tu peen ae
Theke te na jayi meri akh di toheen ae

Munda....
Blue pinde label joint ch green ae

Ni ehtan sada.......

Ni ehtan sada
Ni ehtan sada

Ehtan sada regular mithiye routine aa x4

Kaptaan kaptaan kaptaan kaptaan nu
Harr koi firdi aa nal laike jaan nu
Ishqy crispy ja jatt dekh dekh k
Sohni ton v sohni pandi gabhru nu khaan nu

Puchde aa saare ve ah khand kitho ayi ae
Bnke poison di pand kitho ayi ae
Gol lakk nach nach vaal khull gye ve
Hoke taquilla nal band kitho ayi ae

Jatt vi oh chkke jihdi age eighteen ae

Ehtan sada regular mithiye routine aa x4

Kaatal queen mainu pyar nal aakh de
Mudke ni labbe kyi mere ch gwaach gye
Mera ki ksoor main v rabb ne bnaai aan
Kyi mainu dekh dekh vigad jwaak gye

Nazaran de nazran na paayi jaawe match ni
Aish cash lekhan ch tu karr farmaish ni
Ik do k habbitan khraab baby sadiyan
Peg vich ice aa te chaa ch black ni

Tu high off hoea firre hookeh da shokeen ae

Ni ehtan sada regular mithiye routine aa x4

#gursidhu #jasminesandlas #punjabisong

snippet.title: Ajit Pawar : राष्ट्रवादीच्या आमदारांची मुंबईत जमवाजमव | Sharad Pawar | Maharashtra Politics
snippet.description:
A sudden cancellation of a Pune event by NCP leader Ajit Pawar, coinciding with two top BJP leaders from Maharashtra rushing to Delhi, has set off fresh speculation regarding the plans of the Leader of Opposition in the state. While Shiv Sena (UBT) once again ruled out any possibility of a split in ally NCP, the Eknath Shinde-led Sena said if Ajit Pawar joins hands with the BJP, it will strengthen the state government.

राष्ट्रवादीचे नेते आणि विरोधी पक्षनेते अजित पवार यांच्याबद्दलच्या बातम्यांमुळे राजकीय वातावरण तापले आहे. आता अजित पवारांनी पुरंदर दौरा रद्द केलेला असतानाच राष्ट्रवादीच्या आमदारांची मुंबईत जमवाजमव सुरू असल्याची माहिती समोर आली आहे. राष्ट्रवादीचे काही आमदार मुंबईला निघाले आहे. पक्षाची बैठक असल्याचा आमदारांना निरोप मिळाला आहे. पक्षाचे अध्यक्ष शरद पवार हे पुण्यात असताना मुंबईत बैठक कशी काय असा सवाल उपस्थित केला जात आहे.

Raghu and Prathna travel to Naaglok, where they are shocked to see a dying Swarna. Before her death, Swarna informs the couple that their other daughter is still alive. Will Raghu and Prathna find out their true enemy?

This food challenge is perfect for food #lovers of all levels of price sensitivity. If you're looking for a challenging food challenge that will have you comparing prices and tastes, then this is the video for you! 

Here we'll compare the taste, texture, and overall quality of expensive food vs cheap food. snippet.title: Zigana Pistol से हुई है Atiq Ahmed की हत्या, तुर्किये पिस्टल से निकलती हैं 18 सेकेंड में 20 गोलियां
snippet.description:
Zigana Pistol : प्रयागराज (Prayagraj) से बहुत बड़ी खबर सामने आ रही है। कॉल्विन हॉस्पिटल के पास अतीक अहमद (Atiq Ahmed killed) और अशरफ (Ashraf Ahmed killed) की गोली मारकर हत्‍या कर दी गई। दोनों को मेडिकल कॉलेज लेकर आया गया था। यहीं पर उनकी हत्‍या (atiq ashraf murder) कर दी गई। बताया जा रहा है कि पुलिस ने गोली मारने वाले को पकड़ लिया है। जानकारी के मुताबिक कुछ लोग वहां आए नारे लगाए और फिर गोली मारकर हत्या कर दी गई। इस हमले में एक पुलिस कॉन्‍स्‍टेबल भी घायल हुआ है, जिसका नाम मान सिंह है। उन्हें इलाज के लिए अस्पताल ले जाया गया है।

भारत के सर्वश्रेष्ठ हिंदी न्‍यूज चैनल में से एक जनसत्ता आपके लिए लाता है सभी हिंदी ख़बरें - राजनीति, मनोरंजन, बॉलीवुड, व्यापार और खेल में नवीनतम समाचार। देश दुनिया की ताज़ा खबरों एवं ब्रेकिंग न्यूज के लिए बने रहें जनसत्ता के साथ।

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Click here to watch all your favorite Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gqFEadNxmd8&list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu 

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta' (Shailesh Lodha), is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' (Disha Wakani) and a mischievous son 'Tapu' (Bhavya Gandhi / Raj Anadkat). Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalaal' to call his father 'Champaklal' (Amit Bhatt) from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

---------
Dilip Joshi as Jethalal Champaklal Gada

Many leaders across the country are raising questions on the murder of Mafia Atiq Ahmed during police custody. Foreign media has also covered this murder which happened in public. Most of the foreign media organizations have used the word 'former MP' for Atiq Ahmed in the heading. Also highlighted the murder that took place on live TV. Many institutions have also mentioned the slogans of 'Jai Shri Ram' raised by the accused during the murder. On April 15, Atiq and his brother Ashraf were shot dead while in police custody in Prayagraj.

Without killing Baalveer, Uttan intends to seize his power. To retrieve her Maha Jadoo from Kaashvi, Aageel travels to Udaka Lok. She enters the Udaka Lok by distracting the guards at the entrance. snippet.title: Men's Locker Room Ep 06: KING | Paisa, Sacha Pyaar and Desi Hip-Hop | Part-1 | Tu maan meri jaan
snippet.description:
In this episode, we are in conversation with King, who is a rapper, singer, runner up of MTV Hustle season 1 and with his immensely popular track “Tu maan meri jaan”, has been a phenomenon on billboards.

He talks about why he took on the mononym, and how it’s befitting for him. He also talks about how fame and success have (and in some cases, haven’t) changed his life. He further continues and tells us how differentiating between who’s being real and who’s being fake after your success becomes really important.

He also delightedly shares how and where he spends money the most, and how he prefers to have his own choice and taste in things rather than going with exorbitantly priced things just to fit in. King also tells us how he absolutely loves food, especially his undying love for KFC.

He speaks on relationships being very important to him and how he believes in treasuring the people who were there with him from Day 1.

To know more about the surprisingly humble person, watch the full episode of Men's Locker Room with King

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. snippet.title: Aryan ने बताया Tina को Lovely का सच | Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Full Episode | Ep. 685
snippet.description:
Aryan ने बताया Tina को Lovely का सच | Thapki Pyar Ki | थपकी प्यार की | Full Episode | Ep. 685

Tina finds Aryan speaking to someone about a person named Lovely. She confronts him, and he reveals everything about Lovely. Tina is shocked to see Lovely's picture in a dancer's attire, and she plans to do her own investigation into the matter. Will she come up with something about Lovely?

The bright and beautiful Thapki is pretty much perfect... except for one minor flaw - she stammers. But that doesn't hold her back. All she needs is an encouraging pat on the back,a 'thapki', which soon becomes her name. Over the course of the show, Thapki falls in love with Dhruv, but is duped into getting married to his brother, Bihaan. In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

In spite of this cruel twist of fate, Thapki doesn't let her spirit fade and does all she can to be the ideal bahu. What does destiny hold for this charming girl with an unbeatable spirit?

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah - Ep 3746 - 15 Apr 2023 - Teaser
snippet.description:
Episode 3746: Car Coupon
--------------------------------------------------------
Rustom Ji and his assistant visit the Gada shop to collect the coupons for the lucky draw. At first, Rustom Ji facilitates Jetha with a "certificate of appreciation". Jetha offers some tasty faloodas to Rustom Ji. Jetha deliberately tries to avoid discussions about the coupons, so he brings up irrelevant topics. Anyway, when Rustom Ji asks for the coupons, Jetha gives him all of them except Babita's car coupon. On being asked, Jetha tries to ask Rustom Ji about the consequences if someone has misplaced or damaged the coupon. Rustom Ji informs Jetha that Ramsang Company doesn't qualify them as the winner, and they cancel the prize. What explanation will Jetha give to Babita this time?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah

Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3746, 15 Apr 2023

About The Show
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

►*About*
-------------
RadhaKrishn ke shaashwat prem ke vishay mein to sabhi ko gyaat hai. Radha bina Krishn nahin aur Krishn bina nahin Radha! Yadi Krishn Hriday hain, to Radha us hriday ki gati. Is premi yugal ki is mahagaatha mein aap jaanenge ki kis tarah Radha aur Krishn ne apne prem ko sansaar mein sthaapit kiya aur samast sansaar ko prem ki paribhasha sikhaayi, kyonki prem to bahut se log karte hain kintu keval prem ko paane ke liye… parantu RadhaKrishn ka prem ek-doosre ko paane ke liye nahin, apitu sansaar ko prem sikhaane ke liye tha. To dekhte rahiye RadhaKrishn ki ye anokhi prem-gaatha, jo Krishn nahin, apitu Radha ki drishti se likhee gayi hai!

snippet.title: Naagin 6 | नागिन 6 | Ep. 122 | Highlight | Raghu Apologizes To Prathna!
snippet.description:
Naagin 6 | नागिन 6 | Ep. 122 | Highlight| Raghu Apologizes To Prathna!

Suvarna gets shocked to see Meher and realizes she is Raghu and Prathna's long-lost daughter. Suvarna decides to tell the truth to Raghu and Prathna but is unable to do so. Will she be able to tell Raghu and Pratha the truth?

As Raghu saves Naina's life, Prathna thanks him and expresses her feelings for him. Raghu, however, refuses to forgive her for killing Meher. Elsewhere, Suvarna learns that Meher is Raghu and Prathna's daughter. Will Raghu discover Meher's identity?

Naagin, the saga of love and revenge, sacrifice. This supernatural show traces the lives of 'ichchadhari' naagins. Watch on, as every season, the Naagin fights evil and keeps the ultimate source of power safe.

snippet.title: Tere Bin Ep 32 - [Eng Sub] - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 32 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 13th April 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa
